Quote: Sportswaters enriched with vitamins and minerals are unlikely to improve your performance any more than tap water... Ms Pearce cautions athletes against using sportswaters as a sole energy source in events where additional energy is an advantage: high-intensity sprint training, tournaments, or endurance events.
